msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.146:0.2"
msgid "15. Navapurāṇavagga"
msgstr "15. The Old and the New"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 146. Kammanirodhasutta → kammasuttaṃ (bj) | kammaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.146:0.3"
msgid "146. Kammanirodhasutta"
msgstr "146. The Cessation of Action"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.133"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Navapurāṇāni, bhikkhave, kammāni desessāmi kammanirodhaṃ "
"kammanirodhagāminiñca paṭipadaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you old action, new action, the cessation of "
"action, and the practice that leads to the cessation of action."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmīti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak. …"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.3"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, purāṇakammaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is old action?"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.4"
msgid ""
"Cakkhu, bhikkhave, purāṇakammaṃ abhisaṅkhataṃ abhisañcetayitaṃ vedaniyaṃ "
"daṭṭhabbaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"The eye is old action. It should be seen as produced by choices and "
"intentions, as something to be felt."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.5"
msgid ""
"jivhā purāṇakammā abhisaṅkhatā abhisañcetayitā vedaniyā daṭṭhabbā … pe …"
msgstr "The ear … nose … tongue … body …"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.6"
msgid "mano purāṇakammo abhisaṅkhato abhisañcetayito vedaniyo daṭṭhabbo."
msgstr ""
"mind is old action. It should be seen as produced by choices and intentions, "
"as something to be felt."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, purāṇakammaṃ."
msgstr "This is called old action."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.8"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, navakammaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is new action?"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.9"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, etarahi kammaṃ karoti kāyena vācāya manasā, idaṃ "
"vuccati, bhikkhave, navakammaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The deeds you currently perform by way of body, speech, and mind: this is "
"called new action."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.10"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kammanirodho?"
msgstr "And what is the cessation of action?"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.11"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, bhikkhave, kāyakammavacīkammamanokammassa nirodhā vimuttiṃ phusati, "
"ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammanirodho."
msgstr ""
"When you experience freedom due to the cessation of deeds by body, speech, "
"and mind: this is called the cessation of action."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.12"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, kammanirodhagāminī paṭipadā?"
msgstr "And what’s the practice that leads to the cessation of action?"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.13"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.14"
msgid ""
"sammādiṭṭhi, sammāsaṅkappo, sammāvācā, sammākammanto, sammāājīvo, "
"sammāvāyāmo, sammāsati, sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.15"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammanirodhagāminī paṭipadā."
msgstr "This is called the practice that leads to the cessation of action."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.16"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ mayā purāṇakammaṃ, desitaṃ navakammaṃ, desito "
"kammanirodho, desitā kammanirodhagāminī paṭipadā."
msgstr ""
"So, mendicants, I’ve taught you old action, new action, the cessation of "
"action, and the practice that leads to the cessation of action."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.17"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena "
"anukampaṃ upādāya, kataṃ vo taṃ mayā."
msgstr ""
"Out of compassion, I’ve done what a teacher should do who wants what’s best "
"for their disciples."

msgctxt "sn35.146:1.18"
msgid ""
"Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha, bhikkhave, mā "
"pamādattha; mā pacchāvippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Here are these roots of trees, and here are these empty huts. Practice "
"absorption, mendicants! Don’t be negligent! Don’t regret it later! This is "
"my instruction to you.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.146:1.19"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
